-Navigate through vim by moving the cursor using arrow keys or h(left), j(down), k(up) and l(right) keys.
-To delete a character,place the cursor on the characterto detele and press x. 
-To insert or append a character, press i for insert text and a for appending text.
-When exiting Vim, press <ESC> :q! <ENTER> (Discard all changes)
-Press <ESC> :wq <ENTER> (Save all changes) 
